Zork-Only Commands

The Zork-only command path is intentionally small.

  help [topic]       Read help from /public/docs/zork.
  commands           List available Zork-only shell commands.
  look, l            Look at the Zork portal room.
  gossip <text>      Talk on the global gossip channel.
  egossip <text>     Emote on the global gossip channel.
  gossiphist [n]     Review recent gossip.
  scores             List the top 50 Zork scores.
  quit               Save and disconnect.

After "enter portal", Zork's own parser handles Zork commands such as
look, inventory, take, drop, open, close, read, score, save, restore, and
directions.
